{"tid":2125954,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[讀書分享] 有錢人真係聰明D","createTime":"2020-07-26T14:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T06:48:40.000Z","uid":336299,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b7d1f017d6ceb8d37ed73bd681b9f5fd4dd033","tid":2125954,"uid":336299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x5oEiAT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx5oEiAT.jpg&h=5e70c481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者: Steven D. Levitt<br />\n麻省理工學院經濟學博士，芝加哥大學既經濟學教授<br />\n<br />\n作者認為經濟學的本質: 係一套測量的科學，一組可以測量複雜資訊的完善工具<br />\n佢就想將經濟學的工具應用到更有趣的主題上，書入面研究既題目又真係幾得意下，係到打個目錄比大家睇下:<br />\n<br />\n1: 小學老師和相撲選手的共通點 (金錢和道德操守)<br />\n2: 三K黨和房屋中介的相似之處 (資訊不對稱)<br />\n3: 為何毒販還和母親一起住 (工作薪金低既原因)<br />\n4: 罪犯都跑到哪裡去了? (降低犯罪率的真正因素)<br />\n5: 怎樣才算理想的父母 (影響孩子學業成績的真正因素)<br />\n6: 換個名字會更好?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條片就係講第 5 : 影響孩子學業成績的真正因素  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9VD878DcgCE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9VD878DcgCE&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLle0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=ca967c54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9VD878DcgCE</a><br />\n<br />\n如果大家有咩建議歡迎留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10e665923c3f75ddc7ab772d05b1e1837d648ec","tid":2125954,"uid":210491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18cb5d4e51d3a2ec10738b30e5221f97384e66fb","tid":2125954,"uid":250073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講得幾好，幾流暢<br />\n本書既內容都幾有趣，聽之前都估唔到係咁<img src=\"/